OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a rather cloudy
OL,6,Fstart with the odd spot of rain but
OL,7,Fsoon becoming dry with lengthening
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Feeling warm, especially
OL,9,Fin the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and bright end to the
OL,12,Fday but some patchy low cloud along
OL,13,Fthe Solway coast. Then dry with
OL,14,Flengthening clear spells overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,17,Fsunshine, but some cloud bubbling up
OL,18,Fin the afternoon. Becoming very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
